select oa.guid from(

    select DISTINCT TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000)) as order_date, productName, pogId, subOrderId
    from `all(agCmDump)` 
    where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000))) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 
    and categoryGroup = 'Sexual Wellness' 
    and subCategory = 'Sex Toys & Lingerie') ag
    
    left join (select DISTINCT subOrderId, guid from `temp.Order_Att`) oa
    
    on ag.subOrderId=oa.subOrderId
","temp.guid")

exportSQL(sql="
select distinct a.advId from `temp.guid` g 
left join (select * from (
    SELECT distinct guid, deviceId, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY orderId ORDER BY timestamp ASC) AS Rank
    FROM `last100Days(orderSuccessView)`) where Rank=1 and deviceId IS NOT NULL
) o
on g.guid = o.guid 
LEFT JOIN(
        SELECT DISTINCT deviceId
                        ,advId
        FROM `last100Days(appHeartBeat)`
        ) a
ON a.deviceId = o.deviceId
",path="/Shravya/top_SW_advId_",format="csv",partitions=1,header="true")
